policy.name: Policy for service #23691269, schema_import_test
policy.xml:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<wsp:Policy xmlns:L7p="http://www.layer7tech.com/ws/policy" xmlns:wsp="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/ws/2002/12/policy">
    <wsp:All wsp:Usage="Required">
        <L7p:SchemaValidation>
            <L7p:ResourceInfo staticResourceInfo="included">
                <L7p:Document stringValue="<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<s:schema elementFormDefault="qualified"
    targetNamespace="http://www.acme.com/schemas/purchaseOrder"
    xmlns:accnt="http://www.acme.com/schemas/account"
    xmlns:dd="http://www.acme.com/schemas/delivery" xmlns:s="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema">
    <s:import namespace="http://www.acme.com/schemas/account" schemaLocation="account3.xsd"/>
    <s:import namespace="http://www.acme.com/schemas/delivery" schemaLocation="delivery.xsd"/>
    <s:element name="PurchaseOrder">
        <s:complexType>
            <s:sequence>
                <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1" name="Quantity" type="s:int"/>
                <s:element maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1" name="ItemId" type="s:string"/>
                <s:element ref="accnt:Account"/>
                <s:element ref="dd:Delivery"/>
            </s:sequence>
        </s:complexType>
    </s:element>
</s:schema>
"/>
            </L7p:ResourceInfo>
        </L7p:SchemaValidation>
        <L7p:EchoRoutingAssertion/>
    </wsp:All>
</wsp:Policy>
